beer.beer_description: East meets West in this lightly bitter fusion of IPA and fresh cumquat flavours. Cumquat, you may ask? Hells to the yes to this humble fruit, we say - all hail its aromatic citrus tang! Pair it with Citra and Galaxy hops as we’ve done here and the result is a perfectly balanced summer smasher, with a delightfully dry finish for a truly lip-smacking experience.
